WEBVTT

00:55.097 --> 00:57.558
Did you finish your chores
like I asked?

01:07.359 --> 01:09.028
Outside, let's go.

01:09.069 --> 01:10.571
You, too.

01:37.973 --> 01:40.184
Come get it, assholes.

01:51.529 --> 01:52.905
It's not funny!

12:24.327 --> 12:26.371
Welcome Sheikh Al Radwan.

12:26.413 --> 12:27.622
Go ahead...

12:27.664 --> 12:29.040
Is Sheikh Suleiman home?

12:29.082 --> 12:31.585
I'm afraid he's still away.

12:31.626 --> 12:32.586
When do you expect him
to return?

12:32.627 --> 12:34.171
If you please...

12:34.212 --> 12:36.590
my husband's affairs
are his business.

12:51.521 --> 12:53.023
We picked up a brother
in Aleppo.

12:53.064 --> 12:55.775
Your husband requested
he stay here with you.

12:58.278 --> 12:59.738
Here?

12:59.779 --> 13:01.781
With us?

13:03.492 --> 13:06.578
Like you said...

13:06.620 --> 13:09.039
your husband's affairs
are his business.

13:12.792 --> 13:15.086
When Sheikh Suleiman returns...

13:15.128 --> 13:17.297
tell him Sheikh Al Radwan
wants to see him.

21:17.193 --> 21:20.071
I brought some tea.

21:20.113 --> 21:21.781
Forgive me.

21:21.823 --> 21:23.992
My Arabic isn't good.

23:38.960 --> 23:40.419
Hold still.

23:45.091 --> 23:47.218
Dinner's ready. Let's go!

23:47.260 --> 23:48.761
Go wash up!

23:50.680 --> 23:51.681
Okay, Momma.

28:47.143 --> 28:49.437
Secret Police.
We need your apartment.

30:47.096 --> 30:48.055
Excuse me!

30:48.097 --> 30:49.682
I'm lost. Can you help?

39:42.089 --> 39:43.673
He asked for water,
but we didn't give him anything.

39:43.715 --> 39:44.716
Good.

40:03.068 --> 40:04.194
Open the door.

41:59.017 --> 42:01.937
Take him to the big room.

42:06.399 --> 42:08.985
Take him to the big room.

42:29.506 --> 42:32.884
You're not leaving
until you tell the truth!

42:34.302 --> 42:35.345
I don't know anything.

42:37.222 --> 42:39.516
The transfer,
who did you send it to?

55:16.522 --> 55:18.399
-Watch out behind the door!
-Run!

55:58.564 --> 56:00.816
Get up!

56:52.243 --> 56:55.788
-He's bluffing.
-No.

56:57.540 --> 56:58.958
No. I'm not.

57:01.293 --> 57:02.795
Don't shoot.

57:02.837 --> 57:05.381
Get the keys from the soldier.

57:30.906 --> 57:33.492
Move to the door.
